    public class EditwizardRenderer
extends IFrameRenderer
    Generates an iframe with a wizard list (if the 'list' property is set) or a wizard wizard (if the 'wizard' property is set). Other wizard/list jsp can also be used. E.g. 
    
    Simple examples
    Eenvoudige voorbeelden
    
      
        samples/people
        people>
        firstname,lastname,owner
